description: Experience modern city living in this spacious and beautifully maintained 2-bedroom, 2 full-bathroom bi-level condominium, offering over 1,100 sq ft of thoughtfully designed, open-concept living space. Perfectly situated on the vibrant West Side, this penthouse unit places you just steps from South Boston’s best dining, shopping, and entertainment. Step inside to discover original hardwood floors, elegant custom molding throughout, and an abundance of natural light that fills every corner of the home. The main level features a stylish open kitchen complete with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and an inviting dining area—ideal for entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet meal at home. Upstairs, you’ll find two generously sized bedrooms, each with large walk-in closets, offering comfort and ample storage. This home also features two gas fireplaces, recessed lighting, built-in surround sound, and refined architectural details for a high-end living experience.
